38 //
39 // Box for tracking error bound. This will arise when dynamics decouple into
40 // 1D subsystems. Boxes are defined only by their size in each dimension.
41 //
43 
44 #ifndef FASTRACK_BOUND_BOX_H
45 #define FASTRACK_BOUND_BOX_H
46 
47 #include <fastrack/bound/tracking_bound.h>
48 #include <fastrack/utils/types.h>
49 
50 #include <fastrack_srvs/TrackingBoundBox.h>
51 #include <fastrack_srvs/TrackingBoundBoxResponse.h>
52 
53 namespace fastrack {
54 namespace bound {
55 
56 struct Box : public TrackingBound<fastrack_srvs::TrackingBoundBox::Response> {
57  // Size in each dimension.
58  double x;
59  double y;
60  double z;
61 
62  // Constructors and destructor.
63  ~Box() {}
64  explicit Box()
65  : TrackingBound() {}
66  explicit Box(double xsize, double ysize, double zsize)
67  : TrackingBound(),
68  x(xsize), y(ysize), z(zsize) {}
69 
70  // Convert from service response type SR.
71  inline void FromRos(const fastrack_srvs::TrackingBoundBox::Response& res) {
72  x = res.x; y = res.y; z = res.z;
73  }
74 
75  // Convert to service response.
76  inline fastrack_srvs::TrackingBoundBox::Response ToRos() const {
77  fastrack_srvs::TrackingBoundBox::Response res;
78  res.x = x; res.y = y; res.z = z;
79  return res;
80  }
81 
82  // Visualize.
83  inline void Visualize(const ros::Publisher& pub, const std::string& frame) const {
84  visualization_msgs::Marker m;
85  m.ns = "bound";
86  m.header.frame_id = frame;
87  m.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
88  m.id = 0;
89  m.type = visualization_msgs::Marker::CUBE;
90  m.action = visualization_msgs::Marker::ADD;
91  m.color.a = 0.3;
92  m.color.r = 0.5;
93  m.color.g = 0.1;
94  m.color.b = 0.5;
95  m.scale.x = 2.0 * x;
96  m.scale.y = 2.0 * y;
97  m.scale.z = 2.0 * z;
98 
99  pub.publish(m);
100  }
101 
102 }; //\struct Box
